<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Battalia" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Battalia</orth> (thus Ff; Qq <orth extent="full" opt="n">battalion</orth>), host, army: <cit><quote>our b. trebles that account,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.11" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 V, 3, 11</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>when sorrows come, they come not single spies, but in --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.5.79" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 5, 79</bibl></cit>.
